{"tid":1776252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上水警署不足一個月內　第二度遭掟汽油彈","createTime":"2019-12-09T11:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T01:12:45.000Z","uid":184679,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c31780cd6ff7214829552d91cbe6f858fc1d9b5f","tid":1776252,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:38:29.000Z","msg":"沙頭角公路龍躍頭段8號上水警署，今日(9日)凌晨4時25分，上址的天台及停車場位置冒出熊熊火光，警員查看發現疑遭人投擲汽油彈，地上遺下玻璃碎片，並知會消防到場協助處理，正翻查天眼片段追查歹徒行蹤。<br />\n<br />\n是次為過去不足一個月以來，上水警署第二度遭人掟汽油彈。11月17日凌晨4時48分，上址近停車場位置突現有火光冒竄，消防接報到場開喉將火救熄，調查後認為有縱火成分。警署建築物外牆及泊車處有燒過的痕迹，警方在現場檢獲懷疑汽油彈碎片進一步檢驗，事件中無人受傷。案件列作縱火，交由大埔警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191209/mobile/bkn-20191209044513333-1209_00822_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"a6bbc1239dd0bc38fd1c988c4b320a86b57394ca","tid":1776252,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:39:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc146749fa14108e5fedba6f16b64c36c03a0a3","tid":1776252,"uid":65178,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:39:52.000Z","msg":"強烈遣責 仲未有狗死"},{"pid":"2377c619b7f60930662366120587c53243eac15f","tid":1776252,"uid":46822,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:40:00.000Z","msg":"靜靜雞"},{"pid":"224fbff3007091a51e8496f790cf11073443c2aa","tid":1776252,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:40:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e57f179f6f4d170e0a5ce5c8f179ad6b25723cff","tid":1776252,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T11:42:06.000Z","msg":"胡師父<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\